/*
# Lists
Show bullets
```
<header>
	<ul>
		<li>Important</li>
		<li>Things</li>
		<li>Like <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0084787/">The Thing</a></li>
	</ul>
</header>
```
*/
ul
	list-style-type: disc

li
	margin-bottom: 0.5em

/*
## To-do lists
To-dos have checkboxes and don't need bullets
```
<main>
	<ul>
		<li><label><input type="checkbox" />Dubstep</label><button class="delete">Delete</button></li>
		<li><label><input type="checkbox" />Solves</label><button class="delete">Delete</button></li>
		<li><label><input type="checkbox" />Everything</label><button class="delete">Delete</button></li>
	</ul>
</main>
```
*/
main
	ul
		list-style-type: none
	.delete
		margin-left: 2em

/*
## Completed
```
<p class="done">A thing that is done.</p>
```
*/
.done
	color: gray
	text-decoration: line-through

